      "title": "Under the Indian loan, the last urea will stop",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The last stock of 21,000 metric tons of the 65,000 metric tons of urea fertilizer provided to Sri Lanka under the Indian loan was officially handed over today (22nd) by Indian High Commissioner Ashok Bhagle to Agriculture Minister Mahinda Amaraweera.",
        "The Ministry of Agriculture stated that the work of sending the fertilizer stock to Ceylon Fertilizer Company and Commercial Fertilizer Company has also started."
      ],
